 guild, in which we will build long and lasting relationships, and become an even stronger family! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F3F4F8><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub37.ezboard.com/bchivalrousvalor.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sirdo>Sirdo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guild Master</span><br>  Posts: 96<br> <font color=#273C82>(8/12/03 12:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub37.ezboard.com/fchivalrousvalorfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: raiding and family</span><hr size=1> =)<br>
